{"id":"06b83057-1482-43de-91aa-0ad9da0dfb77","name":"Fenomeno (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(132, 84, 187);\"><strong><em>Meno<br>гѓЎгѓЋ</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">вџЎв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ в„§ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”ЂвџЎ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/bM3lb5VJFyuJ9UvE-aF61.webp\" style=\"width: 510px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">вџЎвљњвџЎв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ в„§ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”ЂвџЎвљњвџЎ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(242, 242, 242);\"><strong><em>An Umamusume with a strong sense of justice, serving the Public Discipline Committee. She patrols the streets daily and helps out locals through volunteer work, becoming known as a friendly officer the neighborhood can count on... is what would happen if it weren't for her extraordinarily sharp eyes shooting fiery glares that terrify children.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(132, 84, 187);\"><strong><em><br>\"Patrol's complete; the perimeters are all clear! I will now shift to guard duty within the academy premises!\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/pyh1_FMRQF8VYKTJ9gvJp.webp\" style=\"width: 456px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">вџЎвљњвџЎв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ в„§ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”ЂвџЎвљњвџЎ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(132, 84, 187);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(132, 84, 187);\"><strong><br><em>1) You met her on your way home from a convenience store.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(132, 84, 187);\"><strong><em>2) You and her go on a afternoon patrol, and found a child.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(132, 84, 187);\"><strong><em>3) Create your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fobxEktfseYMse29oFt67.webp\" style=\"width: 456px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">вџЎвљњвџЎв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ в„§ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”ЂвџЎвљњвџЎ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:<br>And that is Fenomeno done. God, there's too many Fenomeno x Gold Ship art.<br><br>Anyways, here's the 2 polls:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://linkto.run/p/WROSIRHK\" target=\"_blank\">Global/ Soon to come</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://poll-maker.com/poll5591476xE2B54978-164\" target=\"_blank\">JP</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">вџЎвљњвџЎв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ в„§ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”ЂвџЎвљњвџЎ</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/133301739\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/komekome__pp/status/1969022923261280598\" target=\"_blank\">@komekome__pp</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/130875724\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"SVWH9A5f9bGtDfDWojfcl.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["рџ‘©вЂЌрџ¦° Female","рџ“љ Fictional","рџЋ® Game","рџ‘¤ AnyPOV","рџ§¬ Demi-Human","вќ¤пёЏвЂЌрџ©№ Fluff","рџЊ— Switch"],"chats":4065,"messages":66975,"created_at":"2025-09-2